regurgitación.","guid":"ubIlQCkfvIgV2Jk9lRg1kw","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"223","text":"Normal: Apertura\\Nconservada, sin reflujo.","guid":"nsNkNFDj89R4urQtzvjviw","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"223","text":"Estenosis:\\NApertura\\Nreducida.","guid":"BCzgDCCFqvUG0KWb5stSOA","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"223","text":"Insuficiencia:\\NReflujo en diástole.","guid":"U4N6ALbhPBTO0smORgTBhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"222","text":"8.2 Aurícula\\Nizquierda (AI):","guid":"Qx5sbk2afp8urJKjfb_O0w","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"Evaluar tamaño\\Ny función.","guid":"VaZI7Zo1-BxfOKs2Yrolfg","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"Normal: Tamaño normal (diámetro\\N2.7-4.0 cm, área <18 cm²).","guid":"R_iBxEJa6iiPsCh8ZhwWgg","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"Dilatada: Tamaño aumentado,\\Nposible insuficiencia mitral.","guid":"NuQQ7y6300RY-Nann0DPaQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"235","parent":"222","text":"8.3 Ventrículo\\Nizquierdo (VI):","guid":"9kaUDxm0Z3i_EuKkQA_Ufw","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"Evaluar diámetros y\\Ngrosor de paredes.","guid":"raLx_OyWO5IMiCs-1hlNQw","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"Diámetros normales: DVId 4.\\N2-5.8 cm, DVIs <4.0 cm.","guid":"_9qw-hoZAFw_8spx1z0kug","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"235","text":"Grosor de paredes: SIVd\\Ny PPVId <1.1 cm.","guid":"0nmpoiaGR7FoCBPbV3N9Jw","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"235","text":"Motilidad:","guid":"--74mtQ0zdc5vSvZBLWeJg","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"Normal: Motilidad global y\\Nsegmentaria conservadas.","guid":"ew4G_DgauH5tJA9rZmNONA","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"239","text":"Hipocinesia: Disminución de\\Nla motilidad, posible\\Ncardiopatía isquémica.","guid":"wlIPFIgDA2-bY_R5qGgTiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"235","text":"Fracción de\\Neyección (FE):","guid":"wIkUVTeWr_6_J2oeZf12TA","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"Normal: 50-70%\\N(biplano