rvada.","guid":"WtxaWjrX3gAtSKahoT5drA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"PSAP: Medir presión sistólica\\Npulmonar ↪ Normal: <35 mmHg.","guid":"EGEUOq4S-vq-vJSGlwsSKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"222","text":"8.8 Válvula\\Npulmonar (VP):","guid":"AUnf8hV-n2QTSSWimTMSEg","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"Evaluar apertura y\\Nregurgitación ↪ Normal:\\NApertura conservada, sin\\Nreflujo.","guid":"lzZLe1gIjltQc9nQIyWZzQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"222","text":"8.9 Pericardio:","guid":"bDOKzfv7r-xH9LI89w53ng","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"Evaluar grosor y presencia de\\Nlíquido pericárdico.","guid":"AuK0pJScM4CKIbIVaoImbw","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"Normal: Pericardio\\Nnormal, sin derrame.","guid":"pTVF_1Euy7InXlI0cbxQvA","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"Derrame pericárdico: Presencia de\\Nlíquido alrededor del corazón.","guid":"mXd5JmVWLcZE8PVJEN7lXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"222","text":"8.10 Vena cava\\Ninferior (VCI):","guid":"vzaMAZgD01870EIcYrXZCw","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"Medir diámetro y colapso inspiratorio\\N↪ Normal: Diámetro normal con\\Ncolapso adecuado (>50%).","guid":"iOdt9C4Eq1u6GzahR0Z19g","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"222","text":"8.11 Conclusiones:","guid":"Cl20y0SqMjjcH813yB-H6A","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"Normalidad del ETT: Todas\\Nlas estructuras dentro de\\Nlímites normales.","guid":"XPb8RwD2MJdedBKR93NGcw","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"PSAP en el límite superior: 34-35 mmHg,\\Nsin signos de hipertensión pulmonar\\Nclínicamente significativa.","guid":"BL6Eu-bof--tLHnjsqMudg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":271,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"EcoTT PAUTA-2024","id":"map_732","resolved_references":[]}